46:44.802 --> 46:53.744 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DARDIE ROBINSON, Mother: I got a
call out
of the blue from his girlfriend.
And -- sorry

46:53.844 --> 46:58.716 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
-- she said that paramedics were
there working
on Daniel, that she had found
him, that he

46:58.816 --> 47:02.219 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
was blue and unresponsive.

47:02.319 --> 47:05.156 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I told her, I said, "Tell
him his momma
loves him."

47:05.256 --> 47:08.159 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And she said, "Well, I'm sure he
can't hear
you."

47:08.259 --> 47:09.260 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I said, "Tell him anyway."

47:09.360 --> 47:10.661 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
And so she did.

47:10.761 --> 47:14.899 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID WAGNER: In tears, she left
the office
