the call that there was nothing
they could

47:20.538 --> 47:23.708 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
do, and that he was gone.

47:23.808 --> 47:30.281 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID WAGNER: Daniel was 29 and
otherwise
healthy. No one knew why he had
died so suddenly.

47:30.381 --> 47:34.852 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DARDIE ROBINSON: That was, to
